<p class="ql-align-center">说起盛夏，你会想到什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一定会想到狂浪的乐队</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点燃夏日澎湃吧？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去年爆火的综艺《乐队的夏天》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最近王者归来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们的青春躁动又回来啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200812/ff8fb67c042a4f2cac46ca1cff6bfc9d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
